gText_Birch_Welcome::
    .string "Hello there, beautiful MarciBB!\p"
    .string "Welcome to our magical world of POKéMON!\p"
    .string "My name is NYANKEY.\p"
    .string "I'm the POKéMON PROFESSOR here,\n"
    .string "though I may not look like much...\p"
    .string "$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
    .string "You see, MarciBB, our town sent out\n"
    .string "a special request across the regions...\p"
    .string "We desperately needed someone as cute,\n"
    .string "pretty, and angelic as you!\p"
    .string "Our town was... well, let's just say\n"
    .string "we weren't the most attractive bunch.\p"
    .string "But then YOU came! Our savior!\p"
    .string "$"

gText_Birch_MainSpeech::
    .string "I know I'm just a little donkey-like\n"
    .string "professor, not much to look at...\p"
    .string "But ever since you arrived, MarciBB,\n"
    .string "you've brought such beauty and light\l"
    .string "to our humble town!\p"
    .string "The POKéMON here have never been\n"
    .string "happier, and neither have I...\p"
    .string "With your grace and your destined\n"
    .string "talent as a POKéMON master,\l"
    .string "you'll save us all from our ugliness!\p"
    .string "Together, we'll explore this world\n"
    .string "of wonder and maybe... maybe...\p"
    .string "$"

gText_Birch_AndYouAre::
    .string "*blushes* And you are, my beautiful\n"
    .string "angel MarciBB?$"

gText_Birch_BoyOrGirl::
    .string "Wait, I shouldn't assume...\n"
    .string "Are you a boy or a girl, dear MarciBB?$"

gText_Birch_WhatsYourName::
    .string "Perfect! Just as beautiful as I imagined.\n"
    .string "What should I call you, my dear?$"

gText_Birch_SoItsPlayer::
    .string "Ah, {PLAYER}{KUN}... such a lovely name\n"
    .string "for such a lovely person!$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
    .string "Wonderful!\p"
    .string "You're {PLAYER}{KUN}, our savior who came\n"
    .string "to LITTLEROOT TOWN just when we needed\l"
    .string "you most!\p"
    .string "I can hardly contain my excitement\n"
    .string "about all we'll accomplish together!\p"
    .string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
    .string "Are you ready, my dear {PLAYER}{KUN}?\p"
    .string "Your destined role as our town's\n"
    .string "pokemon master and savior begins now!\p"
    .string "Step into the world of POKéMON, where\n"
    .string "adventure, beauty, and... well, maybe\l"
    .string "even romance await!\p"
    .string "I'll be waiting for you at my LAB,\n"
    .string "my precious angel. Please come find me!\p"
    .string "$"
